Roommates themselves, George Rabanca and Ivo Vigan were inspired by their previous roommate mishaps to create a more centralized, cohesive space for New Yorkers to seek and list housing.   rumr focuses on creating a familiar space for users to search within, making social connectivity an integral part of its service. Listings are virtual open houses where users can view not only available rooms, but also potential roommates—a task made simple with rumr’s Invite Roommates feature.
